How do I find past releases of validator_cli.jar?
I found https://oss.sonatype.org/#nexus-search;quick~org.hl7.fhir.validation.cli
but it just goes to 5.0.0. I was using version 5.1.5 last fall, and the current version is 5.2.20.
I'd like to compare output from past versions to the current one.
The tooling/releases stream here may also be informative.
